			take your seat as Winter continues.
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Next|History Lesson]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>

	<<elseif $rightarm is "bound" or $leftarm is "bound" or $feetuse is "bound">>
