		<br><br>

		<<link [[Next|Hallways]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
		<br><br>
	<<else>>
		<<npc Winter>><<person1>>
		Winter looks at your clothing. "You can't have believed I wouldn't notice. Go see the head."
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Next|Hallways]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
